data.description: Beautifully remodeled 4 bedroom home located in desirable Highlands West! Great open concept with gorgeous hardwood floors on the main level. Kitchen features granite counters, stainless appliances and plenty of cabinet space. The walkout lower level has a large family room, recreation room, full bath and a bedroom - could make an ideal in-law arrangement. Sliders from the main level lead to a huge deck with a patio below - perfect for relaxing or entertaining. There's a large seperate workshop with a private entrance behind the garage - could be ideal for a home based business!
